data.description: Beautifully and immaculately kept home on 1 acre of land with fantastic location in Haines City.  This home offers an open and spacious layout that has been expanded and updated with tile flooring, a large rear screened in porch, an inviting front deck, an outdoor kitchen with gas stove and sink, a storage shed, and a bonus HUGE 16'ft high workshop/garage measuring almost 1000 square feet!  Inside the split floorplan offers privacy and convenience for everyone.  The dining room-family room combo is perfect for gatherings, and the owner's suite and bathroom has a garden tub to relax at the end of the day, a separate shower, and a walk-in closet.   Fruit trees, shade, a car port, and lots of outdoor space for all your recreational needs makes this the perfect place to call home! Call today and schedule your private showing right away!  Surrounded by lakes and country, yet so close to everything you need, homes like this don't last long!
